*《威塞克斯故事集》Wessex Tales (1888, a collection of short stories)
*《一群高貴的淑女》A Group of Noble Dames (1891, a collection of short stories)
*《生活的小諷刺》Life's Little Ironies (1894, a collection of short stories)

